I would write these foolproof plays in my little green notebook that I had.

825
00:54:01,208 --> 00:54:03,672
對手甚至不知道怎麼被打敗的
- The opposition didn't even know what hit 'em. - [Door Knocking]

826
00:54:04,410 --> 00:54:05,907
