so you might as well let the damn thing go, 'cause if you don't,

839
00:54:51,293 --> 00:54:53,457
我就會對你不客氣，不客氣
it's gonna get awfully, awfully physical around here.

840
00:54:54,162 --> 00:54:56,960
我想你也不想那樣吧？是吧？
and I don't think you want that, do you? Huh?

841
00:54:59,172 --> 00:55:01,037
