泥狗隊迎來了第三節比賽
[Musburger] The Mud Dogs are faced with yet another third and long.

1104
01:12:32,661 --> 01:12:34,258
- 衝啊！ - Grenouille回傳
- Hut! - Grenouille back to pass.

1105
01:12:34,863 --> 01:12:39,062
他又被困在原地！ 泥狗隊進攻時不能把球傳出去。
He's gonna be stuffed again! and the Mud Dogs offence is still unable to move that ball.

1106
01:12:40,269 --> 01:12:42,800
他們的防守十分的出色， 他們還有贏得勝利的機會
But the way their defense is fired up, they still have a shot at winning this game.

1107
01:12:43,569 --> 01:12:45,166
Blake，過來。聽著
Blake, come here. Look.

1108
01:12:45,806 --> 01:12:48,537
現在，我們要做的是……
Now, what if we, uh-- [Whispering]

1109
01:12:51,411 --> 01:12:54,042
相信我。上，上，上，上，上
Trust me. Go, go, go, go, go. [Evil Laughter]

1110
01:12:54,915 --> 01:12:58,447
第三節時間過半，美洲獅隊27:7領先
[Musburger] The Cougars lead 27-7 in the middle of the third quarter.

1111
01:12:59,487 --> 01:13:01,084
犯規了？
- and he takes a knee? - [Whistle Blows]

1112
01:13:01,622 --> 01:13:04,587
你們要幹什麼啊？
- Y'all gonna play or what? - [Chattering]

1113
01:13:05,460 --> 01:13:08,058
你們對我的新戰術怎麼看？
[Laughing] How do you all like my new offence?

1114
01:13:11,800 --> 01:13:13,264
好吧，這是第二和12
[Musburger] all right, it's second and 12...

1115
01:13:13,802 --> 01:13:16,667
- 美洲獅隊開球。 - 衝啊！
- as the Cougars line up on the ball. - Hut! Hut!

1116
01:13:17,547 --> 01:13:19,078
[Whistle Blows]

1117
01:13:19,642 --> 01:13:22,173
Red Beaulieu的球隊要幹嘛，消極進攻嗎？
What is Red Beaulieu doing, refusing to play offence?

1118
01:13:22,978 --> 01:13:25,142
- Dan，這很奇怪 - 不奇怪，Brent。
- Dan, this is bizarre. - [Dan] No, it's not, Brent.

1119
01:13:25,782 --> 01:13:28,413
這很聰明，因為Red把茶水男孩排除出比賽之外了
It's brilliant, because Red is taking the waterboy out of the game.

1120
01:13:29,286 --> 01:13:31,250
就靠犯規然後開球這戰術，
By kneeling down three times and punting,

1121
01:13:31,921 --> 01:13:33,485
他使泥狗隊無法順利進攻
he's gonna make the Mud Dog offence try to beat him.

1122
01:13:33,990 --> 01:13:35,887
不過他們今天的比賽方式，是很難忍受的
and the way they're playing today, that's impossible.

1123
01:13:36,460 --> 01:13:38,090
沒錯，這使泥狗隊最有價值的球員
[Musburger] Well, the Mud Dog's most valuable player,

1124
01:13:38,628 --> 01:13:41,126
那個被稱為「茶水男孩」的後衛， 現在無用武之地
the linebacker they call ''the Waterboy,'' is now powerless.

1125
01:13:41,965 --> 01:13:46,064
看來Klein教練要找其他的辦法來對付Red
That means Coach Klein will have to find another way to outfox Red.

1126
01:13:47,204 --> 01:13:50,669
泥狗隊暫停
- [Whistle Blows] - [Man] Mud Dogs call a time-out.

1127
01:13:51,742 --> 01:13:53,806
Klein教練，Klein教練！
- [Cheering, Indistinct] - Mr. Coach Klein. Mr. Coach Klein!

1128
01:13:54,513 --> 01:13:56,644
Klein教練！
Mr. Coach Klein!

1129
01:13:57,282 --> 01:14:00,581
- 你要去哪兒？ - 我想去吃塊餅
- Where are you going? - I was just gonna get a hot pretzel.

1130
01:14:01,586 --> 01:14:03,817
Klein教練，你怕Red Beaulieu嗎？
Mr. Coach Klein, are you afraid of Red Beaulieu?

1131
01:14:04,529 --> 01:14:06,594
[Laughing, Shouting]

1132
01:14:08,291 --> 01:14:09,755
我把他嚇倒了
I am petrified of him.

1133
01:14:10,260 --> 01:14:12,658
那麼，你為什麼不把Red Beaulieu想像成……
Well, why don't you pretend that Red Beaulieu...

1134
01:14:13,430 --> 01:14:15,127
那些你不怕的人呢？
is somebody that you're-you're not afraid of.

1135
01:14:15,666 --> 01:14:17,797
- 想像成？ - 是的
- pretend? - Yes.

1136
01:14:18,503 --> 01:14:20,534
想像成那些你不怕的人
Visualize somebody you're not afraid of.

1137
01:14:21,206 --> 01:14:23,670
- 然後攻擊，就像你告訴我的一樣 - 我試試
- and then attack, like you told me. - I'll try.

1138
01:14:24,441 --> 01:14:26,739
他現在就在哪兒
Well, he's right over there.

1139
01:14:32,524 --> 01:14:34,756
[Chuckling]

1140
01:14:38,790 --> 01:14:40,487
小嬰孩
Little baby.

1141
01:14:41,026 --> 01:14:42,957
是的
Yeah.

1142
01:14:43,629 --> 01:14:47,495
你好，小孩
Hello, little baby. [Baby Talking]

1143
01:14:51,169 --> 01:14:53,433
要奶嘴？你沒有奶嘴啊？
a poo-poo? Do you have a poo-poo?

1144
01:14:54,140 --> 01:14:55,570
是的
Yes.

1145
01:14:56,108 --> 01:14:58,005
好的。那麼現在
Okay. Now.

1146
01:14:58,677 --> 01:15:00,541
這就是我們接下來要做的。 他應該會在這出現……
This is what we're gonna do. He's gonna come here--

1147
01:15:01,154 --> 01:15:03,119
[Chattering, Shouting]

1148
01:15:09,222 --> 01:15:11,686
來吧，美洲獅
Come and get this one, Cougars.

1149
01:15:12,426 --> 01:15:14,290
紅色，22號！開球！
Red, 22! Hike!

1150
01:15:14,861 --> 01:15:17,225
球傳給了Grenouille。一個背後球！
[Musburger] Snap to Grenouille. a reverse!

1151
01:15:18,031 --> 01:15:20,963
不，是兩個背後傳球！ 哦，奇跡啊！
No, it's a double reverse! Oh, what a block!

1152
01:15:21,835 --> 01:15:23,265
Boudier的戰術失靈了
and Boudier springs free!

1153
01:15:23,804 --> 01:15:27,570
被阻擋！分邊！拿到球了！太精彩了！
Trouble! Lateral! Got him! What a play!

1154
01:15:28,676 --> 01:15:31,641
Grenouille到了15碼區！10碼區！5碼區！
Grenouille to the 15! To the 10! To the 5!

1155
01:15:32,545 --> 01:15:34,342
- 泥狗隊觸地得分！ - 哦，哦，哦
- Touchdown, Mud Dogs! - [Fouts] Well, well, well.

1156
01:15:35,014 --> 01:15:37,078
我猜Klein的袖子裡有神奇
I guess Coach Klein does have a few tricks up his sleeve after all.

1157
01:15:37,752 --> 01:15:40,483
這是……這是什麼？嗯？
What the hell-- What the hell is this? Huh?

1158
01:15:41,322 --> 01:15:44,020
我們可是個冠軍球隊啊！
We go from a championship football team to a bunch of dogs!

1159
01:15:44,858 --> 01:15:47,556
現在，我們把鏡頭移向邊線， 我們的記者，Lynn Swann
Right now, we're going to go down to the sidelines and our man, Lynn Swann.

1160
01:15:48,396 --> 01:15:50,060
Swannie，你給我們帶來了什麼？
Swannie, what do you have for us?

1161
01:15:50,665 --> 01:15:52,129
我跟Vicki Vallencourt在一起， 在這場重要比賽裡
I'm with Vicki Vallencourt, who's taking over...

1162
01:15:52,667 --> 01:15:54,998
她接管了Bobby Boucher茶水員工作
Bobby Boucher's water duties for this important game.

1163
01:15:55,771 --> 01:15:58,135
哦，我不是接替。 我只是盡力不把這弄得更糟
Oh, I'm not takin' over. I'm just tryin' not to screw up too bad.

1164
01:15:58,873 --> 01:16:01,504
那麼，問你個問題。 你能預測下比賽的結果嗎？
Well, let me ask you this. What's your prediction for the rest of this ball game?

1165
01:16:02,311 --> 01:16:03,908
泥狗隊30:27獲勝
Mud Dogs are gonna win, 30 to 27.

1166
01:16:04,446 --> 01:16:06,577
真是有意思。你怎麼會這麼猜呢？
That's very interesting. How'd you come up with that guess?

1167
01:16:07,282 --> 01:16:09,947
猜？那才不是猜呢！這就會是結果
Guess? That ain't no guess! That's what it's gonna be.

1168
01:16:10,752 --> 01:16:13,083
- 好的。沒事。 - 哦！在那兒小心點，Swannie。
- Okay. That's fine. - Oh! Be careful down there, Swannie.

1169
01:16:17,226 --> 01:16:19,290
好吧。 Meaney。Meaney在哪兒？
all right. Meaney. Where's Meaney?

1170
01:16:19,929 --> 01:16:21,393
- Meaney？ - 在這兒，教練
- Meaney? - Here, Coach.

1171
01:16:21,965 --> 01:16:24,796
- 上去看看茶水男孩能拿你怎麼辦 - 是的，先生！
- Get in there and let's see if that waterboy can stop you. - Yes, sir!

1172
01:16:25,601 --> 01:16:28,966
Red把他最好的防守球員派上場啦
Red is sending his best defender in as a running back?

1173
01:16:29,974 --> 01:16:31,938
你怎麼看呢，Dan？
What do you make of this, Dan?

1174
01:16:32,543 --> 01:16:34,307
嗯，Brent，我想他是想 找個辦法來抑制茶水男孩
Well, Brent, he's gotta find some way to neutralize the waterboy.

1175
01:16:34,945 --> 01:16:37,610
他可能認為Meaney會擺平那傢伙的
He probably thinks that Meaney will just pound it in there like Fridge used to do for the Bears.

1176
01:16:38,449 --> 01:16:41,314
嘿，茶水男孩！你女朋友還會再一次救你嗎？
Hey, Waterboy! Is your girlfriend gonna save you again?

1177
01:16:42,186 --> 01:16:43,883
哦，不用，先生。 我會靠我自己來解決問題的。
Oh, no, sir. I'm gonna take matters into my own hands.

1178
01:16:44,422 --> 01:16:47,654
- 你會看到的 - 你去死吧！你這個SB！哇哦！
- You'll see. - Bring it to the hole! Your ass is mine! Whoo!

1179
01:16:48,627 --> 01:16:50,891
哇哦！哇哦！
Whoo! Whoo!

1180
01:16:51,629 --> 01:16:53,259
你的叫聲就像是個破火車
You sound like a... a big choo-choo train.

1181
01:16:53,798 --> 01:16:56,529
哇哦！
Whoo! [Groans]

1182
01:17:03,640 --> 01:17:06,371
重磅炸彈，感謝Insano上校
power bomb, compliments of Captain Insano.

1183
01:17:10,754 --> 01:17:13,153
* Let's go fight with your might **

1184
01:17:13,917 --> 01:17:16,148
好吧，射門得分，射門得分。上！
all right, field goal. Field goal. Go.

1185
01:17:16,819 --> 01:17:19,484
- Derek。Derek！ - 在
- Derek. Derek! - Yeah.

1186
01:17:20,325 --> 01:17:22,823
設想一下進攻。去開球。開球。
Visualize the attack. Go kick the ball. Kick it.

1187
01:17:23,594 --> 01:17:24,991
開球！
- Hut! - [all Grunting]

1188
01:17:26,964 --> 01:17:28,628
你能做什麼，小子？
How you doin', boy? [Laughing]

1189
01:17:29,167 --> 01:17:31,164
不，不，不！
No, no, no! [Screaming]

1190
01:17:34,546 --> 01:17:36,611
[Cheering, Shouting]

1191
01:17:44,490 --> 01:17:46,622
[Whimpering]

1192
01:17:51,697 --> 01:17:54,997
[players Shouting, Indistinct]

1193
01:17:55,962 --> 01:17:57,726
那是什麼啊？
What the hell is that?

1194
01:18:04,270 --> 01:18:07,068
那是什麼——他在搞什麼？ 怎麼這裡面沒有！嗯？
Where the hell is-- What the hell is he up to? That ain't in here! Huh?

1195
01:18:07,907 --> 01:18:09,337
嘿！
- [Cheering] - Hey!

1196
01:18:09,842 --> 01:18:11,439
第四節兩隊比分還相差10分
[Musburger] Down by ten late in the fourth quarter,

1197
01:18:12,012 --> 01:18:14,009
Klein教練選擇射門得分.
Coach Klein opts for the field goal.

1198
01:18:14,682 --> 01:18:17,513
然後他們需要個不越位的射門 和一個觸地得分來扳平比分
[Fouts] Then they have to hope for the onside kick and a touchdown to tie the game.

1199
01:18:18,352 --> 01:18:21,717
Dan，看場上。 Boucher看來負責清道
Dan, look what we have here. Boucher's in the game as a blocker.

1200
01:18:22,690 --> 01:18:24,487
這是今年最後一場球了，Brent。 現在任何事情都會發生
Last game of the year, Brent. Can't hold anything back now.

1201
01:18:27,694 --> 01:18:29,625
準備！
Set!

1202
01:18:33,167 --> 01:18:34,697
回傳。這是假象！
The snap. It's a fake!

1203
01:18:38,705 --> 01:18:41,370
Boucher跑在前面！撞得好！
Boucher's out in front! a great block!

1204
01:18:42,210 --> 01:18:44,808
第二個了！
- [Grunting] - and a second one!

1205
01:18:45,646 --> 01:18:47,610
泥狗隊觸地得分！
Touchdown, Mud Dogs!

1206
01:18:48,183 --> 01:18:50,948
- Boucher帶球得分！ - 啊！
- Boucher led him all the way! - [Screaming] Yeah!

1207
01:18:54,122 --> 01:18:55,619
Red Beaulieu生氣了，Dan。
Red Beaulieu is steaming, Dan.

1208
01:18:56,158 --> 01:18:57,989
Brent，他看到他完美的一個 賽季就這麼快被破壞了
Brent, he sees his perfect season slipping away.

1209
01:18:58,627 --> 01:19:01,458
美洲獅隊只領先3分了
The Cougar's lead is down to three.

1210
01:19:02,371 --> 01:19:05,904
[Cheerleaders Cheering, Indistinct]

1211
01:19:06,869 --> 01:19:09,467
泥狗隊可能會先把比分扳平，然後再打加時賽
The Mud Dogs need the ball back if they're gonna have a shot at overtime.

1212
01:19:10,305 --> 01:19:13,136
Bobby Boucher現在處在開球方陣
and Bobby Boucher is now on the kickoff team.

1213
01:19:14,043 --> 01:19:16,908
- 今年最後一場球了，Brent。現在任何事情都會發生 - 我知道
- Last game of the year, Brent. Can't hold anything back now. - I know.

1214
01:19:17,713 --> 01:19:20,378
下個是誰呢？
- [Horns Blaring] - Who's it gonna be?

1215
01:19:21,251 --> 01:19:24,082
該是誰呢？ 該是誰呢？
Who's it gonna be? Who's it gonna be?

1216
01:19:28,156 --> 01:19:30,554
哦，是的。就是你了。
[Chuckling] Oh, yeah. There's my bitch.

1217
01:19:31,327 --> 01:19:33,291
注意了，球至少要前進10碼
[Musburger] Remember, the ball must travel ten yards.

1218
01:19:36,366 --> 01:19:37,930
那很輕鬆！
It's loose!

1219
01:19:38,469 --> 01:19:40,867
- 泥狗隊控球！泥狗隊控球！ - 很好！
-Mud Dogs football! Mud Dogs football! -all right!

1220
01:19:41,672 --> 01:19:43,302
媽媽，我拿到球了！我拿到……
Mama, I got the football! I got it--

1221
01:19:43,872 --> 01:19:45,936
哦，多麼不道德的一擊！ 犯規啦！
Oh, what a vicious hit! That was a cheap shot.

1222
01:19:46,609 --> 01:19:48,006
哦！
- Oh! - [Murmuring]

1223
01:19:48,510 --> 01:19:50,474
一個無聲的判罰
- [Whistle Blowing] - [Fouts] and what a dumb penalty.

1224
01:19:51,080 --> 01:19:53,678
泥狗隊要射門得分來扳平比分
That puts the Mud Dogs in field goal range for the tie.

1225
01:19:54,517 --> 01:19:57,282
- Dan，我不確定Boucher能不能再站起來 - 哦，我的兒子！
- Dan, I'm not sure that Boucher is able to get back up. - Oh, my baby!

1226
01:20:05,062 --> 01:20:06,726
它還是很涼
It's still cold. [Chuckles]

1227
01:20:07,298 --> 01:20:09,562
借過！借過！
- [Chattering] - Excuse me. Out of my way.

1228
01:20:13,604 --> 01:20:15,735
Dan，你不希望看到這發生
Dan, you hate to see this happen.

1229
01:20:24,716 --> 01:20:27,047
那可是高質量的水哦
Now, that's high quality H2O.

1230
01:20:27,819 --> 01:20:30,984
繼續比賽！來吧，Bobby！
- [Cheering] - [Vicki] You go on, now! Make it happen, Bobby!

1231
01:20:35,927 --> 01:20:37,624
茶水男孩救只需要些水就行
The waterboy just needed some water.

1232
01:20:38,197 --> 01:20:41,829
- 喔哦，Dan。你想那是你的功勞嗎？ - 閉嘴，Brent。
- Wow, Dan. You think that up all by yourself? - Shut up, Brent.

1233
01:20:46,072 --> 01:20:47,402
你沒事吧？
- [Shouting, Yelling] - are you okay?

1234
01:20:47,940 --> 01:20:49,637
他想讓我痛苦的號叫，我不會讓他得逞的
He tried to open up a can of whoop-ass on me. I wouldn't let him.

1235
01:20:50,177 --> 01:20:53,142
聽著，最後的比賽我有個新的戰術。 你以前從沒做過的。
Listen, I have an idea for the last play. You haven't done this before.

1236
01:20:54,047 --> 01:20:55,511
怎麼樣？這麼來進攻開球
all right? The offence is gonna line up like this.

1237
01:20:56,050 --> 01:20:57,514
- 好的 - 你剛好到這兒
- Yeah. - You're gonna be right here.

1238
01:20:58,052 --> 01:20:59,782
今天這兒不會有平局
[Musburger] There'll be no tie here today.

1239
01:21:00,354 --> 01:21:03,219
Klein教練正在佈置他的進攻戰術
Coach Klein is sending his offence back on to the field.

1240
01:21:04,092 --> 01:21:05,722
他將會贏的比賽
He's going for the win right now.

1241
01:21:06,327 --> 01:21:07,757
是的，這才是勇敢者的呼聲，Brent
[Fouts] Yeah, this is a real gutsy call, Brent.

1242
01:21:08,293 --> 01:21:09,823
英雄還是狗熊就看此一招了
He'll either be a hero or a goat because of this.

1243
01:21:10,328 --> 01:21:13,994
還有，Dan，Bobby Boucher回到場上了
[Musburger] and Dan, Bobby Boucher is back on the field.

1244
01:21:15,100 --> 01:21:18,198
他現在司值進攻！ 我們知道，我們知道
He is now playing offence! We know. We know.

1245
01:21:19,138 --> 01:21:21,769
Meaney，如果他們把球傳給茶水男孩
Meaney, if they give that Waterboy the football,

1246
01:21:22,509 --> 01:21:24,006
我是不會介意你是否去傷害他的！
I don't care if you have to stab him!

1247
01:21:24,544 --> 01:21:26,308
不能放過他。明白了嗎？
Do not let him get away. Do you understand me?

1248
01:21:26,913 --> 01:21:29,845
- 是的，教練！ - 明白了嗎？上場去！
- Yes, sir. Yes, sir! - Do you understand me? Get in there!

1249
01:21:30,751 --> 01:21:32,582
加油！
[all] Break!

1250
01:21:39,627 --> 01:21:42,959
- 我準備好了，朋友 - 讓我們來搞定它，Bobby
- I'm ready, friend. - Let's do it, Bobby.

1251
01:21:44,999 --> 01:21:46,930
準備！準備！
